# Design System Guardrails

- For any UI/design task, strictly follow the existing design system already in this repository.
- Reuse existing components, tokens, spacing, typography, and interaction patterns before introducing anything new.
- Keep visual and behavioral consistency with the current system; do not invent a parallel style language.
- Do not edit `app/globals.css`.
- If styling changes are needed, implement them with component-level patterns that align with the established system instead of changing global CSS.
